text: Yokohama Mazu temple The is a temple of the Chinese sea goddess Mazu located in Yokohama, Japan. It opened on 17 March 2006.. It is located in Yokohama's Chinatown. ==References== ==External links== * . & Category:Yokohama Category:Temples of Mazu Category:Taoist temples in Japan
